emotes.msg: I see you have already learned all that I can teach you. Please leave me be.

Use this gem and you will fall prey to the most critical of strikes far less often than your peers. But mind you, read the gem's inscription before you use it. There is a cost associated with powers such as these.
Come visit me sometime and perhaps we can practice your newfound ability.
